Package Model

Class Pharmacist

java.lang.Object
Model.Staff
Model.Pharmacist
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Pharmacist extends Staff
The Pharmacist class represents a specific type of Staff member in the hospital management system. This class extends the Staff class and sets the role to StaffType.PHARMACIST.

It provides constructors to initialize a pharmacist with default or specific details.

Features:

  • Default constructor for creating a generic pharmacist with default values.
  • Parameterized constructor for creating a pharmacist with specific details such as name, password, gender, age, and hospital ID.

      Parameterized constructor for the Pharmacist class.

      This constructor initializes a Pharmacist object with specific details such as name, password, gender, age, and hospital ID. The role is automatically set to StaffType.PHARMACIST.
